r their important science engineering and business problems by attracting developing exciting and rewarding exceptional people that will build shareholder value our vision  exponent’s vision is to engage the brightest scientists and engineers to empower clients with solutions for a safe healthy sustainable and technologically advanced world exponent is traded on the nasdaq exchange stock symbol expo  please visit our investor relations page for specific information on the financial performance of the firm   for a current stock quote and summary data click here investor relations our history failure analysis associates faaa was founded in palo alto california in  when three professors from stanford university and two engineers from stanford research institute sri decided to pioneer a new field  investigating how and why failures and accidents occur faaa initially provided engineering expertise to the legal and insurance industry in the ’s the company continued to expand its accident investigation services while also responding to the increased engineering requirements of the utility and nuclear power industries in the ’s the company added new engineering and science disciplines including civil engineering structural engineering electrical engineering biomechanics data analysisstatistics human factors and visual communication services we were wellknown and respected for our independent investigations on some of worlds biggest engineering accidents and failures and we expanded our office footprint outside of california read more exponent has worked on a number of wellknown investigations over its nearly  years in business many of these projects have been featured in print cable or online click here to learn more about these investigations wellknown investigations iso certification and gsa information quality the hallmark of exponent services  to confirm our commitment to quality exponents quality management system is independently assessed against the most recognized a